def domain_name(url):

def domain_name(url):
    url = url.replace("http://", '')
    url = url.replace("https://", '')
    url = url.replace("www.", '')
    last = url.rfind('/')
    
    if last is not None:
        url = url[:last]
        
    dot = url.find('.')
    
    if dot is not None:
        url = url[:dot]
        
    return url

import re
def domain_name(url):    
    g = re.sub('((http|https)\:\/\/)?(www.)?', '',url)
    s = re.search('[a-zA-Z0-9-]*.', g)
    
    return s.group()[:-1]

def domain_name(url):
    import re
    result = re.sub('^.*//|www\.', '', url) # del 'http://' and 'www.' (start of url)
    result = re.sub('\..*', '', result)     # del .com, .co.jp, ... (end of url)
    return result
